definition: to come/to arrive/to come round/ever since/next

sentences.english: The sources of Chinese medicine are mainly floras, also includes animals and mineral.
sentences.chinese: 中藥的來源主要是植物，也有一些動物和礦物。

sentences.english: This paper based on the boiler rebuild project of DaLian Maritime University.
sentences.chinese: 本課題來源於大連海事大學的鍋爐房改建工程。

sentences.english: Many of these can be derived from the schematics or the memory configuration of your target hardware.
sentences.chinese: 許多這些可以來源於圖表或對內存配置的目標硬件。

sentences.english: What is the origin of pelagic oozes ?
sentences.chinese: 遠洋軟泥的來源是什麼？

sentences.english: Some argue that it originates from the Zulu for 'making a loud noise'.
sentences.chinese: 有人說是來源於祖魯語中“製造噪音”的說法。

sentences.english: These camp robbers hae become habituated to campers as a food source.
sentences.chinese: 這些營地掠奪者已經慣於將野營者作爲一種食物來源。

sentences.english: Is natural diet right for your ferret ?
sentences.chinese: 自然的飲食來源對貂是好的嗎？

sentences.english: Also a good source of vegetarian protein.
sentences.chinese: 同時也是植物蛋白的好來源。

sentences.english: They say part of their income comes from the registration fee.
sentences.chinese: 他們稱他們部分收入來源於掛號費。

sentences.english: Anomalous refraction is believed to be the main error source for classical astrometry.
sentences.chinese: 反常折射已成爲傳統天體測量學的主要誤差來源。

sentences.english: This model is generated on a primary human fibroblast-derived dermal matrix.
sentences.chinese: 這個模型產生於人成纖維來源的模型。

sentences.english: Scientists believe it is a main source of the G ring and its single ring arc.
sentences.chinese: 科學家認爲，它是一個主要來源國和它的單環環弧。

sentences.english: You can use the “source” links to read more on each battle.
sentences.chinese: 你可以點擊“來源”鏈接，閱讀這些戰爭的更多內容。

sentences.english: Wikileaks.org, which published the documents, won't reveal its source.
sentences.chinese: org作爲發佈這些文件的網站，不願透露其來源。

sentences.english: Nowadays people look to technology as an alternative source of satisfaction.
sentences.chinese: 現在人們指望科技能成爲滿足感的另一個來源。

sentences.english: The crown is the source of oxygen, worker of the magic of photosynthesis.
sentences.chinese: 樹冠是氧的來源，是神奇光合作用的製造者。
